---
title: Plant-Based Crumbed Chick'n & Couscous Bowl with Roasted Veggies & Almonds
description: Root veggies like potato and beetroot can really bring a new layer to couscous. Top it with plant-based chick'n that’s crumbed
and golden. We’ll let you go and enjoy this delicious meal!
